1
00:00:49,299 --> 00:00:51,968
STILL SHINING

2
00:00:56,556 --> 00:00:58,016
<i>Benarkan saya ucap selamat tinggal</i>

3
00:00:59,809 --> 00:01:01,936
<i>kepada Tae-seo depan-depan sebelum pergi.</i>

4
00:01:06,524 --> 00:01:09,027
<i>Saya tahu kamu semua takkan keluar</i>
<i>kalau cuaca sejuk.</i>

5
00:01:10,612 --> 00:01:11,446
<i>Tapi…</i>

6
00:01:13,698 --> 00:01:14,866
Mo Eun-a.

7
00:01:28,797 --> 00:01:35,428
STILL SHINING

8
00:01:40,850 --> 00:01:44,354
Semua tempat di pekan ini
nampak sama saja di mana pun.

9
00:01:45,563 --> 00:01:47,232
Kita dah makin dekat?

10
00:01:54,864 --> 00:01:56,741
Kelip-kelip…

11
00:01:57,575 --> 00:02:00,036
Saya tahu kelip-kelip tak keluar
ketika cuaca sejuk, tapi…

12
00:02:00,120 --> 00:02:01,079
Apa awak…

13
00:02:03,414 --> 00:02:05,333
buat di sini?

14
00:02:14,050 --> 00:02:15,051
Hei, bukankah itu Tae-seo?

15
00:02:15,969 --> 00:02:16,803
Tae-seo!

16
00:02:21,724 --> 00:02:23,017
Im A-sol, turun.

17
00:02:24,769 --> 00:02:26,396
Tae-seo, awak pandu kereta!

18
00:02:26,479 --> 00:02:28,565
Awak tahu restoran itu di mana!

19
00:02:28,648 --> 00:02:30,108
Jalan di sini mengelirukan!

20
00:02:30,191 --> 00:02:31,234
Saya penat!

21
00:02:33,945 --> 00:02:35,488
Saya dah pandu sampai ke sini!

22
00:02:35,572 --> 00:02:37,407
Saya penat!

23
00:02:40,618 --> 00:02:42,287
Dia bercakap dengan siapa?

24
00:02:46,791 --> 00:02:48,376
Saya sejuk!

25
00:02:49,460 --> 00:02:50,420
Geramnya.

26
00:02:52,755 --> 00:02:53,631
Aduhai.

27
00:03:02,098 --> 00:03:03,725
Dia sikit pun tak berubah.

28
00:03:04,309 --> 00:03:06,019
Dulu saya selalu jaga dia.

29
00:03:06,102 --> 00:03:07,520
Orang fikir dia adik saya.

30
00:03:07,604 --> 00:03:09,689
Rupa dia lagi seiras saya, bukan Tae-seo.

31
00:03:09,772 --> 00:03:12,984
Apa pula? Dia Tae-seo versi comel.

32
00:03:13,067 --> 00:03:14,694
Ramai orang cakap begitu.

33
00:03:15,528 --> 00:03:16,738
Cuma perangai lain.

34
00:03:16,821 --> 00:03:18,281
A-sol, biar saya tuang.

35
00:03:18,364 --> 00:03:20,700
Terima kasih sebab jemput kami.

36
00:03:20,783 --> 00:03:22,619
- Nampak sedap.
- Sedap, bukan?

37
00:03:22,702 --> 00:03:26,497
<i>Ramyeon</i> makanan laut
dan <i>kimchi</i> lama di sini sedap.

38
00:03:26,581 --> 00:03:28,833
Sebab saya datanglah
dia keluarkan <i>kimchi</i> lama.

39
00:03:30,877 --> 00:03:32,921
Tae-seo terus tinggalkan Seoul demi awak.

40
00:03:33,004 --> 00:03:34,672
Dia tak teragak-agak pun.

41
00:03:34,756 --> 00:03:36,215
Sekarang baru saya faham.

42
00:03:36,299 --> 00:03:38,343
Di Seoul, dia selalu nampak penat.

43
00:03:38,426 --> 00:03:40,303
Tapi di sini ada lautan,

44
00:03:40,386 --> 00:03:42,013
langit cerah, udara segar.

45
00:03:43,306 --> 00:03:45,266
Seronok di sini.

46
00:03:46,309 --> 00:03:48,102
Itu maksud awak rupa-rupanya.

47
00:03:48,186 --> 00:03:50,647
"Ayah saya kerja tengok langit,

48
00:03:50,730 --> 00:03:52,690
mak saya tengok langit dan laut."

49
00:03:52,774 --> 00:03:55,068
Dia kata kerja mereka
yang terbaik dalam dunia.

50
00:03:55,985 --> 00:03:58,029
Itu ayat yang mak selalu cakap.

51
00:03:58,112 --> 00:03:59,447
Abang ingat lagi?

52
00:03:59,530 --> 00:04:01,616
Mestilah dia ingat.

53
00:04:01,699 --> 00:04:04,285
Kali terakhir jumpa,
awak masih bertongkat.

54
00:04:04,369 --> 00:04:05,828
Dah boleh berjalan elok.

55
00:04:05,912 --> 00:04:08,665
Sudahlah, itu cerita lama.

56
00:04:09,457 --> 00:04:12,293
- Ayah awak sihat?
- Lebih daripada sihat.

57
00:04:12,377 --> 00:04:14,128
Hei, jangan.

58
00:04:14,212 --> 00:04:16,130
Awak kena pandu balik ke Seoul.

59
00:04:16,214 --> 00:04:17,715
Saya nak ke hospital.

60
00:04:17,799 --> 00:04:18,800
Abang.

61
00:04:19,550 --> 00:04:20,385
Balik sajalah.

62
00:04:21,052 --> 00:04:24,180
Tetamu abang datang,
hantarlah mereka balik ke Seoul.

63
00:04:24,264 --> 00:04:26,641
Hyeong-seok pun datang.
Dia tak pernah datang.

64
00:04:26,724 --> 00:04:28,768
Dia nak minum pun rasa kekok.

65
00:04:28,851 --> 00:04:30,645
Adik saya rindukan saya, ya?

66
00:04:31,229 --> 00:04:32,438
Minumlah.

67
00:04:32,522 --> 00:04:34,565
Awak dah besar, dah boleh minum arak.

68
00:04:34,649 --> 00:04:35,483
Malulah saya.

69
00:04:42,156 --> 00:04:44,701
Lampu basikal dia rosak.

70
00:04:46,327 --> 00:04:48,621
Wanita berbasikal tadi
bekas kekasih awak, bukan?

71
00:04:54,294 --> 00:04:55,545
Dia tinggal di Gangneung.

72
00:04:56,629 --> 00:04:57,463
Bukan.

73
00:05:00,008 --> 00:05:01,301
Jadi, dia tinggal di mana?

74
00:05:02,343 --> 00:05:03,511
Saya tak tahu.

75
00:05:05,096 --> 00:05:06,306
Kenapa dia ke sini?

76
00:05:08,224 --> 00:05:09,934
Tak tahu.

77
00:05:10,018 --> 00:05:11,644
Awak tak sempat bercakap dengan dia.

78
00:05:13,021 --> 00:05:15,732
Mesti awak geram dan tertanya-tanya.

79
00:05:41,340 --> 00:05:43,885
MO EUN-A

80
00:05:44,469 --> 00:05:46,262
MO EUN-A

81
00:05:48,765 --> 00:05:50,767
<i>Kenapa awak ada di Yeonwoo…</i>

82
00:06:33,392 --> 00:06:35,144
Tae-seo datang.

83
00:06:37,105 --> 00:06:38,397
Ya, saya datang.

84
00:06:40,358 --> 00:06:42,652
Mesti sukar buat kamu.

85
00:06:43,736 --> 00:06:47,740
Rehatlah cukup-cukup
sementara cuti khidmat tentera.

86
00:06:52,453 --> 00:06:53,287
Apa ini?

87
00:06:54,330 --> 00:06:55,915
Cakaplah kalau nak datang.

88
00:06:55,998 --> 00:06:58,126
Saya tak sempat makan pun tadi.

89
00:06:58,209 --> 00:07:00,211
Abang dapat bercakap dengan nenek?

90
00:07:01,462 --> 00:07:03,381
Dia cakap pasal masa abang dalam tentera.

91
00:07:03,464 --> 00:07:05,508
Dia cakap pasal masa saya sekolah.

92
00:07:05,591 --> 00:07:06,884
Masa berlalu bagi dia.

93
00:07:10,680 --> 00:07:13,057
Ada nampak Eun-a di rumah hujung itu?

94
00:07:13,850 --> 00:07:15,268
Kenapa tiba-tiba sebut nama dia?

95
00:07:17,103 --> 00:07:17,937
Rasa macam nampak dia.

96
00:07:20,314 --> 00:07:21,607
Saya tak nak abang lemah.

97
00:07:23,609 --> 00:07:26,821
Hidup saja macam biasa.
Kahwin dan dapat anak.

98
00:07:26,904 --> 00:07:28,114
Balik jarang-jarang.

99
00:07:28,197 --> 00:07:29,407
Susah sangatkah?

100
00:07:29,490 --> 00:07:30,741
Saya akan hidup sendiri,

101
00:07:30,825 --> 00:07:34,078
kemudian hantar datuk nenek
jumpa mak ayah.

102
00:07:34,162 --> 00:07:35,163
Saya akan buat semua.

103
00:07:35,246 --> 00:07:37,039
Abang tanya nampak dia tak?

104
00:07:37,123 --> 00:07:38,541
Cakap benda lain pula.

105
00:07:39,584 --> 00:07:40,918
Pergi dulu.

106
00:08:05,318 --> 00:08:06,444
Maaf.

107
00:08:19,582 --> 00:08:22,793
Eun-a patut dah sampai, tapi dia lewat.

108
00:08:22,877 --> 00:08:25,338
Dia keluar naik basikal buruk itu.

109
00:08:26,214 --> 00:08:28,049
Awak kena cari dia cepat.

110
00:08:29,967 --> 00:08:31,719
Ya.

111
00:11:16,509 --> 00:11:17,760
Apa awak buat di sini?

112
00:11:17,843 --> 00:11:20,513
Saja datang tengok sekolah sekejap.

113
00:11:21,347 --> 00:11:22,681
Saya tak tahu dah tutup.

114
00:11:23,349 --> 00:11:24,475
Bukan.

115
00:11:24,558 --> 00:11:26,977
Kenapa di sini? Yeonwoo.

116
00:11:29,647 --> 00:11:31,065
Awak akan tinggal di sini?

117
00:11:32,233 --> 00:11:33,484
Taklah, sekejap saja.

118
00:11:36,195 --> 00:11:37,780
Saya akan tinggal dengan Park So-hyeon.

119
00:11:40,324 --> 00:11:41,659
Baguslah.

120
00:11:41,742 --> 00:11:44,328
Walaupun risau terserempak
dengan awak di sini,

121
00:11:44,412 --> 00:11:48,416
saya tetap nak beritahu saya akan pergi
tinggal dengan Park So-hyeon.

122
00:11:50,292 --> 00:11:51,627
Saya nak ucap selamat tinggal

123
00:11:52,753 --> 00:11:54,547
dan saya nak beritahu depan-depan.

124
00:11:56,424 --> 00:11:57,508
Saya dah dapat buat.

125
00:11:59,427 --> 00:12:01,387
Lampu basikal saya rosak.

126
00:12:01,470 --> 00:12:03,806
Awak ikut saya dari belakang.

127
00:12:04,890 --> 00:12:06,434
Baguslah.

128
00:12:06,517 --> 00:12:08,936
Saya risau saya kena balik tolak basikal.

129
00:12:09,019 --> 00:12:11,689
Ingat simpang jalan
yang kita selalu berpecah?

130
00:12:12,356 --> 00:12:13,899
Kita ucap selamat tinggal di sana.

131
00:12:14,608 --> 00:12:16,652
Saya nak buat begitu dengan awak.

132
00:12:18,154 --> 00:12:18,988
Baguslah.

133
00:12:21,574 --> 00:12:22,658
Bila awak berangkat?

134
00:12:23,325 --> 00:12:25,035
Tak lama lagi.

135
00:12:26,745 --> 00:12:27,830
Alang-alang jumpa,

136
00:12:29,206 --> 00:12:30,291
kita ucap selamat tinggal.

137
00:12:31,459 --> 00:12:33,502
Saya memang nak ucap depan-depan.

138
00:12:35,463 --> 00:12:36,839
Selamat tinggal.

139
00:12:39,717 --> 00:12:40,885
Saya pergi dulu.

140
00:15:14,830 --> 00:15:15,831
Ini saya.

141
00:15:19,084 --> 00:15:20,252
Saya tahu.

142
00:15:23,130 --> 00:15:24,673
Tak ada apa-apa berlaku, bukan?

143
00:15:26,342 --> 00:15:27,718
<i>Saya…</i>

144
00:15:27,801 --> 00:15:31,430
<i>Saya tinggal awak sendirian</i>
<i>dengan rakan sekerja awak itu.</i>

145
00:15:33,474 --> 00:15:35,809
Tak ada apa-apa masalah, bukan?

146
00:15:37,978 --> 00:15:39,146
<i>Kenapa…</i>

147
00:15:40,314 --> 00:15:42,107
Kenapa risau tentang saya?

148
00:15:44,360 --> 00:15:45,819
Tak perlu pun.

149
00:15:48,447 --> 00:15:50,115
<i>Awak tak perlu</i>

150
00:15:52,117 --> 00:15:53,702
risau apa-apa.

151
00:15:57,122 --> 00:15:58,499
Tak perlu risau…

152
00:16:00,125 --> 00:16:01,794
<i>Mungkin betul.</i>

153
00:16:01,877 --> 00:16:05,005
<i>Saya masih boleh bayangkan</i>
<i>padang itu dengan jelas,</i>

154
00:16:06,256 --> 00:16:08,425
saya tertanya-tanya
adakah awak dah selesai.

155
00:16:10,636 --> 00:16:13,806
Adakah tinggalkan tempat
yang awak dah curahkan sepenuh hati

156
00:16:14,932 --> 00:16:16,475
tak terlalu menyakitkan

157
00:16:19,061 --> 00:16:21,188
<i>dan kenapa awak sering dipaksa pergi</i>

158
00:16:22,731 --> 00:16:24,984
<i>sedangkan awak tak pernah nak pergi.</i>

159
00:16:27,653 --> 00:16:28,737
Memang tak perlu,

160
00:16:32,491 --> 00:16:35,119
tapi saya tertanya-tanya.

161
00:16:41,709 --> 00:16:43,544
Kenapa Park So-hyeon mak awak?

162
00:16:43,627 --> 00:16:45,337
<i>Itu sebab</i>

163
00:16:45,421 --> 00:16:48,590
saya anggap mak dia macam nenek saya.

164
00:16:50,217 --> 00:16:51,218
Orangnya baik.

165
00:16:51,927 --> 00:16:55,764
<i>Awak tak buat pilihan yang salah</i>
<i>sebab rasa terperangkap, bukan?</i>

166
00:16:56,557 --> 00:16:59,685
- Kalau awak rasa terperangkap…
<i>- Tak, Tae-seo.</i>

167
00:17:03,105 --> 00:17:04,481
<i>Saya ke Tongyeong.</i>

168
00:17:05,232 --> 00:17:07,276
Rumah tamu awak dah tutup,

169
00:17:07,943 --> 00:17:09,903
<i>saya diberitahu</i>
<i>awak pergi ke rumah mak awak.</i>

170
00:17:10,904 --> 00:17:13,741
<i>Saya ingatkan mak yang tinggal jauh</i>

171
00:17:14,700 --> 00:17:16,410
yang suka makan mi itu.

172
00:17:17,786 --> 00:17:19,288
Kita saling terlepas.

173
00:17:20,914 --> 00:17:22,666
<i>Kita selalu begitu.</i>

174
00:17:26,295 --> 00:17:28,297
RUMAH LAMA IM A-SOL

175
00:17:39,016 --> 00:17:40,059
Saya kena letak.

176
00:17:40,142 --> 00:17:41,477
<i>Nanti nenek bangun.</i>

177
00:17:41,560 --> 00:17:42,936
Saya letak dulu.

178
00:17:45,230 --> 00:17:46,065
Eun…

179
00:17:56,658 --> 00:18:00,621
Saya ada tiga acara
termasuk mesyuarat dan parti akhir tahun.

180
00:18:00,704 --> 00:18:02,498
Tempat itu tak jauh,

181
00:18:02,581 --> 00:18:04,166
jadi saya singgah.

182
00:18:07,127 --> 00:18:08,337
Awak minum?

183
00:18:09,338 --> 00:18:11,006
Ya, sikit.

184
00:18:12,466 --> 00:18:13,300
Maaf.

185
00:18:14,760 --> 00:18:16,303
Kenapa minta maaf pula?

186
00:18:19,473 --> 00:18:20,516
Nak saya pergi?

187
00:18:21,100 --> 00:18:22,434
Kalau penat, saya pergi.

188
00:18:25,729 --> 00:18:27,689
Mari kita keluar minum.

189
00:18:27,773 --> 00:18:29,108
Saya nak cakap dengan awak.

190
00:18:32,152 --> 00:18:34,613
Saya nak habiskan apa yang kita tengok.

191
00:18:35,906 --> 00:18:36,865
Boleh.

192
00:18:40,994 --> 00:18:42,913
Saya ternampak <i>bungeoppang</i> masa ke sini.

193
00:18:42,996 --> 00:18:44,498
Tapi tak ada parkir.

194
00:18:45,415 --> 00:18:46,291
Nanti saya belikan.

195
00:18:50,003 --> 00:18:50,838
Awak duduklah.

196
00:18:50,921 --> 00:18:51,755
Okey.

197
00:19:27,124 --> 00:19:27,958
Seronok.

198
00:19:31,420 --> 00:19:36,550
Seronok duduk santai begini
lepas penat bekerja.

199
00:19:43,265 --> 00:19:44,725
Satu teguk saja.

200
00:19:44,808 --> 00:19:46,268
Saya boleh tinggal kereta.

201
00:19:55,444 --> 00:19:56,278
Fokus.

202
00:20:10,167 --> 00:20:13,337
HAE-JIN

203
00:20:14,338 --> 00:20:17,758
<i>Hai, Eun-a. Maaf telefon lewat malam.</i>

204
00:20:17,841 --> 00:20:18,800
Ada hal penting.

205
00:20:18,884 --> 00:20:20,969
Boleh ganti saya tiga jam esok?

206
00:20:21,553 --> 00:20:24,598
<i>Awak cuma perlu daftar masuk</i>
<i>satu tetamu pukul 3.00 petang.</i>

207
00:20:49,957 --> 00:20:51,792
Aduhai, maaf buat awak tunggu.

208
00:20:51,875 --> 00:20:53,627
Banyak kereta atas jalan.

209
00:20:53,710 --> 00:20:56,380
Nak kerja beberapa jam pun
awak bersiap elok.

210
00:20:56,463 --> 00:20:58,131
Memang profesional.

211
00:20:58,215 --> 00:20:59,716
Awak nak makan apa?

212
00:20:59,800 --> 00:21:01,260
Saya belanja, jom.

213
00:21:01,343 --> 00:21:03,220
Saya kena kejar bas.

214
00:21:03,303 --> 00:21:05,138
Awak datang untuk tolong saya saja?

215
00:21:05,889 --> 00:21:07,516
Terharunya.

216
00:21:08,558 --> 00:21:10,394
Betul bukan nak jumpa sesiapa?

217
00:21:13,605 --> 00:21:15,023
Ada, bukan?

218
00:21:15,774 --> 00:21:18,110
Saya dah agak.
Kalau nak jumpa dia, jumpalah.

219
00:21:24,324 --> 00:21:25,450
Dah jumpa.

220
00:21:27,452 --> 00:21:29,579
<i>Orang yang saya nak jumpa,</i>
<i>walaupun sekejap.</i>

221
00:21:33,417 --> 00:21:35,127
Saya dah jumpa dia.

222
00:21:56,648 --> 00:22:01,153
YEON NAMSAN

223
00:22:30,557 --> 00:22:31,433
<i>So-hyeon.</i>

224
00:22:32,726 --> 00:22:34,811
<i>Saya mungkin sampai lewat.</i>

225
00:22:35,437 --> 00:22:36,688
<i>Nanti saya beritahu.</i>

226
00:23:51,471 --> 00:23:53,098
<i>Sampai di sini.</i>

227
00:24:05,193 --> 00:24:07,988
<i>Cuba selamatkan hubungan,</i>

228
00:24:09,698 --> 00:24:11,950
<i>ganggu hidup awak yang tenang,</i>

229
00:24:13,827 --> 00:24:15,412
<i>dan ulang kitaran kejam ini.</i>

230
00:24:15,495 --> 00:24:16,580
<i>Cukup.</i>

231
00:24:27,591 --> 00:24:29,092
<i>Awak dah gila?</i>

232
00:24:29,176 --> 00:24:32,262
<i>Tahu rugi berapa kalau batalkan</i>
<i>penerbangan sekarang?</i>

233
00:24:32,345 --> 00:24:34,306
<i>Di hotel awak bekerja 10 tahun lalu,</i>

234
00:24:34,389 --> 00:24:36,725
<i>rakan sekerja awak</i>
<i>dah jadi penolong pengurus.</i>

235
00:24:36,808 --> 00:24:40,145
<i>Mereka semua tunggu awak balik,</i>

236
00:24:40,228 --> 00:24:41,897
<i>lagi-lagi mak saya.</i>

237
00:24:41,980 --> 00:24:43,982
<i>Semua orang tunggu awak.</i>

238
00:24:46,693 --> 00:24:48,153
<i>Saya akan pergi macam dirancang.</i>

239
00:24:49,404 --> 00:24:51,656
<i>Saya akan kotakan janji.</i>

240
00:24:55,327 --> 00:24:56,578
<i>Ayah.</i>

241
00:24:56,661 --> 00:25:00,373
<i>Masa ayah suruh saya nikmati hidup</i>
<i>macam sedang mengembara,</i>

242
00:25:01,249 --> 00:25:04,544
<i>maksud ayah, kita tak boleh kekal</i>
<i>walaupun kita nak.</i>

243
00:25:05,128 --> 00:25:07,255
<i>Apa yang nampak macam</i>
<i>akan kekal selamanya, tidak.</i>

244
00:25:09,549 --> 00:25:12,135
<i>Sebab hidup penuh</i>
<i>dengan perkara tak kekal,</i>

245
00:25:12,219 --> 00:25:14,054
<i>apabila tiba masanya untuk pergi,</i>

246
00:25:14,804 --> 00:25:17,349
<i>maksud ayah, saya mesti melangkah,</i>
<i>macam mengembara.</i>

247
00:25:20,435 --> 00:25:24,731
<i>Kini pada usia 30 tahun, baru saya faham.</i>

248
00:25:34,449 --> 00:25:37,118
PANGGILAN TAK DIJAWAB
EUN-A

249
00:25:46,795 --> 00:25:48,672
PASAR MINI

250
00:25:52,384 --> 00:25:53,218
Sejuk di luar.

251
00:26:00,850 --> 00:26:02,018
Tunggu sekejap.

252
00:26:41,933 --> 00:26:46,646
<i>Masa saya dan ayah mula-mula datang,</i>
<i>kami bawa satu beg saja.</i>

253
00:26:47,397 --> 00:26:49,274
<i>Ada dalam almari bilik utama.</i>

254
00:26:49,357 --> 00:26:51,067
<i>Dalam laci paling bawah.</i>

255
00:26:51,151 --> 00:26:53,361
<i>Beg galas orang guna untuk mendaki.</i>

256
00:26:54,821 --> 00:26:57,198
<i>Boleh tolong ambil?</i>

257
00:27:17,594 --> 00:27:19,137
Yang ini, betul?

258
00:27:19,220 --> 00:27:20,680
Ya, betul.

259
00:27:24,434 --> 00:27:27,020
Saya bawa yang ini pun dah cukup.

260
00:27:27,103 --> 00:27:29,856
Ingatkan saya takkan dapat
ambil apa-apa dari sini.

261
00:27:29,939 --> 00:27:31,399
Sebab awak, saya dapat ambil.

262
00:27:34,778 --> 00:27:36,821
Awak tak pernah ke dapur kami, bukan?

263
00:27:36,905 --> 00:27:38,490
Ini ruang terbaik rumah kami.

264
00:27:38,573 --> 00:27:40,742
Awak bukan telefon saya nak tunjuk dapur.

265
00:27:43,578 --> 00:27:45,997
Saya ke Seoul sebab saya ada hal.

266
00:27:46,748 --> 00:27:49,042
Sebab itu Seoul, Yeon Namsan ada di sana.

267
00:27:49,918 --> 00:27:51,544
Saya teringat awak, saya telefon.

268
00:27:54,089 --> 00:27:55,757
Saya telefon tanpa fikir,

269
00:27:56,841 --> 00:27:58,426
tapi apabila nampak awak di sini,

270
00:27:58,510 --> 00:28:00,095
saya rasa saya faham kenapa.

271
00:28:01,638 --> 00:28:04,265
Saya nak buat begini dengan awak.

272
00:28:08,395 --> 00:28:09,604
Mari kita ke sana.

273
00:28:21,991 --> 00:28:23,368
Ini awak punya.

274
00:28:34,963 --> 00:28:37,215
Akhirnya saya dapat pelawa awak teh.

275
00:28:43,179 --> 00:28:44,305
Saya…

276
00:28:46,307 --> 00:28:48,184
berangkat hari Jumaat.

277
00:28:52,355 --> 00:28:53,273
Cepatnya.

278
00:29:04,743 --> 00:29:07,912
Betul cakap awak. Saya rasa terperangkap,
Park So-hyeon jadi mak saya.

279
00:29:10,206 --> 00:29:12,500
Sebab itu jadi begitu.

280
00:29:16,796 --> 00:29:18,506
Dengan kata lain,

281
00:29:19,924 --> 00:29:22,010
saya dapat buat keputusan sebab awak.

282
00:29:25,847 --> 00:29:29,350
Dah lama saya fikir mungkin
saya patut terima dia sebagai keluarga.

283
00:29:29,976 --> 00:29:33,313
Setidaknya ayah saya tinggalkan
Park So-hyeon sebelum dia pergi.

284
00:29:34,105 --> 00:29:35,398
Saya fikir begitu.

285
00:29:38,067 --> 00:29:39,569
Bukan salah awak,

286
00:29:40,612 --> 00:29:41,821
tapi sebab awak.

287
00:29:43,198 --> 00:29:45,033
Selalu sebab awak.

288
00:29:48,536 --> 00:29:50,163
Akhirnya semua sebab awak.

289
00:29:51,331 --> 00:29:54,501
Tapi awak mungkin rasa sebaliknya
tentang saya.

290
00:29:55,710 --> 00:29:56,753
Kalau awak pergi…

291
00:29:59,130 --> 00:30:00,423
awak akan kembali?

292
00:30:00,507 --> 00:30:02,091
Sekarang,

293
00:30:02,675 --> 00:30:04,302
tiada rancangan begitu.

294
00:30:07,096 --> 00:30:08,556
Awak akan tinggal di mana?

295
00:30:08,640 --> 00:30:10,099
Rumah mak Park So-hyeon.

296
00:30:10,183 --> 00:30:12,060
Wanita yang akan jadi nenek saya.

297
00:30:12,143 --> 00:30:13,478
Mereka tak tinggal bersama.

298
00:30:13,561 --> 00:30:14,437
Kerja pula?

299
00:30:14,521 --> 00:30:16,564
Saya boleh terus kerja.

300
00:30:18,733 --> 00:30:20,527
Park So-hyeon cakap

301
00:30:20,610 --> 00:30:24,113
hotel tempat saya kerja
10 tahun lalu tunggu saya,

302
00:30:25,824 --> 00:30:26,825
jadi saya patut pergi.

303
00:30:27,951 --> 00:30:31,287
Tak sangka mereka masih ingat saya.

304
00:30:31,371 --> 00:30:32,622
Saya suka hotel itu.

305
00:30:33,414 --> 00:30:34,374
Tapi…

306
00:30:35,708 --> 00:30:37,418
Kalau saya tak ke sana…

307
00:30:42,841 --> 00:30:44,092
Kalau saya tak pergi…

308
00:30:47,762 --> 00:30:50,056
Itu yang saya fikir
sepanjang 10 tahun lepas.

309
00:30:53,893 --> 00:30:55,979
Tapi sekarang saya dah boleh balik.

310
00:31:02,110 --> 00:31:03,611
Awak ada tempat tinggal,

311
00:31:04,779 --> 00:31:06,281
nenek awak ada di sana

312
00:31:07,115 --> 00:31:08,741
dan awak akan ada kerja.

313
00:31:17,041 --> 00:31:17,959
Kenapa…

314
00:31:19,085 --> 00:31:20,879
awak pergi ke Tongyeong?

315
00:31:22,714 --> 00:31:26,342
Saya tak faham kenapa kita begini.

316
00:31:29,429 --> 00:31:30,680
Semua serba tak kena.

317
00:31:31,723 --> 00:31:33,558
Awak ada sebab nak berpisah.

318
00:31:34,767 --> 00:31:36,895
Keputusan masa umur saya
20 tahun itu salah,

319
00:31:38,313 --> 00:31:39,397
tapi keputusan awak betul.

320
00:31:47,322 --> 00:31:48,448
Awak sedar

321
00:31:48,531 --> 00:31:50,867
kita saling risau sekarang?

322
00:31:52,201 --> 00:31:53,286
Sebab bagi kita,

323
00:31:54,621 --> 00:31:56,289
kita tak nak saling susahkan.

324
00:31:58,541 --> 00:32:00,043
Tak kira kita di mana.

325
00:32:05,673 --> 00:32:07,634
Dalam dunia ini, awak saja yang begitu.

326
00:32:13,848 --> 00:32:16,976
Saya beritahu saya log masuk
akaun awak dengar lagu dua kali.

327
00:32:18,269 --> 00:32:19,520
Dua-dua kali di sini.

328
00:32:26,069 --> 00:32:27,904
SENARAI LAGU

329
00:32:27,987 --> 00:32:29,739
<i>Ketika itu bulan Disember.</i>

330
00:32:31,407 --> 00:32:34,202
<i>Saya selesema selepas kaut salji</i>
<i>di seluruh kampung.</i>

331
00:32:35,370 --> 00:32:37,455
<i>Saya putuskan</i>
<i>untuk buat latihan di Hawaii.</i>

332
00:32:41,000 --> 00:32:43,920
<i>Akhirnya saya terima kita dah berpisah.</i>

333
00:32:46,798 --> 00:32:51,094
<i>Kemudian, apabila saya lepaskan segalanya</i>
<i>di Tongyeong dan datang ke sini,</i>

334
00:32:51,678 --> 00:32:53,179
<i>sebelum pergi ke Seoul…</i>

335
00:32:55,723 --> 00:32:57,642
<i>Apabila saya log masuk ke akaun awak…</i>

336
00:33:00,853 --> 00:33:01,813
Pandang saya.

337
00:33:03,064 --> 00:33:06,609
<i>…rasa macam saya sedang pandang awak.</i>

338
00:33:10,363 --> 00:33:11,698
Walaupun saya jauh,

339
00:33:12,907 --> 00:33:16,119
kalau saya kena pinjam kekuatan awak,
saya log masuk akaun awak.

340
00:33:17,996 --> 00:33:19,247
Awak tak kisah, bukan?

341
00:33:21,416 --> 00:33:22,375
Kalau awak pergi,

342
00:33:24,335 --> 00:33:25,378
awak akan senyum begitu?

343
00:33:30,633 --> 00:33:32,385
Saya tak suka dia.

344
00:33:34,429 --> 00:33:37,015
Dia ceria, tak tahu apa yang menanti.

345
00:33:39,809 --> 00:33:41,144
Saya suka dia.

346
00:33:45,857 --> 00:33:46,941
Kalau begitu…

347
00:33:50,403 --> 00:33:52,155
saya kena cuba jadi macam dia.

348
00:33:54,490 --> 00:33:55,616
Saya akan cuba.

349
00:33:59,120 --> 00:34:00,079
Baik saya pergi.

350
00:35:19,450 --> 00:35:21,661
Eun-a, mari makan.

351
00:35:24,122 --> 00:35:27,125
Nenek seronok dapat masak untuk kamu.

352
00:35:27,834 --> 00:35:29,877
Saya dah siap sapu. Banyak kerja di sini.

353
00:35:30,711 --> 00:35:32,338
Hari ini nak buat apa?

354
00:35:33,422 --> 00:35:34,757
Saya nak singgah ke rumah.

355
00:35:35,591 --> 00:35:37,635
Saya nak bersihkan dapur.

356
00:35:39,095 --> 00:35:40,513
Kamu nak masuk ke dalam?

357
00:35:42,640 --> 00:35:43,808
Ke dapur saja.

358
00:35:45,768 --> 00:35:47,854
Saya tahulah, nanti saya datang.

359
00:35:50,523 --> 00:35:52,733
- Terima kasih banyak.
- Semoga berjaya.

360
00:35:52,817 --> 00:35:54,152
Sama-sama.

361
00:36:29,896 --> 00:36:31,898
Saya ingat nombor ini dah tak wujud.

362
00:36:32,982 --> 00:36:36,444
<i>Dong-sik kata awak nak tinggalkan Korea.</i>

363
00:36:36,527 --> 00:36:37,612
Tak lama lagi.

364
00:36:38,613 --> 00:36:41,699
<i>Kalau ada nak cakap apa-apa, cakaplah.</i>
<i>Mesti awak benci saya.</i>

365
00:36:53,711 --> 00:36:55,796
<i>Saya tak layak nak cakap,</i>

366
00:36:55,880 --> 00:36:57,715
<i>tapi masa itu saya sangka awak tinggal</i>

367
00:36:57,798 --> 00:36:59,926
<i>rumah tamu yang awak sayang sebab dia.</i>

368
00:37:00,509 --> 00:37:03,179
Saya sangat marah, tertanya-tanya
untuk apa segala usaha saya.

369
00:37:04,388 --> 00:37:06,515
<i>Namun setelah saya tenang…</i>

370
00:37:08,017 --> 00:37:11,479
- Pada waktu itu<i>…</i>
<i>- Saya tak rancang nak ke sana jumpa dia.</i>

371
00:37:11,562 --> 00:37:13,981
Saya memang terserempak
dengan dia di Seoul.

372
00:37:16,609 --> 00:37:19,362
Saya berusaha sebaik mungkin
untuk tamatkan apa yang saya mulakan.

373
00:37:21,322 --> 00:37:23,032
<i>Walaupun awak takkan percaya.</i>

374
00:37:24,075 --> 00:37:25,660
Itu yang awak nak cakap?

375
00:37:27,536 --> 00:37:29,163
<i>Tapi yalah, biasalah terserempak.</i>

376
00:37:29,956 --> 00:37:31,582
<i>Ingat budak yang saya pernah bercinta?</i>

377
00:37:31,666 --> 00:37:33,251
Budak rumah awak masa latihan.

378
00:37:34,627 --> 00:37:36,087
Saya ingat.

379
00:37:36,170 --> 00:37:39,215
Dia kata awak nampak lain
pakai seragam hotel

380
00:37:39,298 --> 00:37:41,050
dan pakai pakaian biasa.

381
00:37:41,634 --> 00:37:44,428
<i>Dia kata awak tak sesuai</i>
<i>pakai pakaian biasa. Merepek.</i>

382
00:37:44,512 --> 00:37:46,180
Awak pun cakap begitu.

383
00:37:47,014 --> 00:37:49,058
<i>Awak kata alasan itu merepek.</i>

384
00:37:50,434 --> 00:37:53,562
<i>Saya terserempak bekas kekasih</i>
<i>di Gangneung di Pulau Geoje.</i>

385
00:37:54,480 --> 00:37:55,856
Memang boleh berlaku.

386
00:37:56,857 --> 00:37:58,276
<i>Sepanjang hidup,</i>

387
00:37:58,359 --> 00:38:01,570
<i>awak orang pertama yang betul-betul dengar</i>

388
00:38:02,738 --> 00:38:05,032
dan menghormati saya.

389
00:38:07,243 --> 00:38:08,494
Saya bukan sesiapa istimewa.

390
00:38:09,537 --> 00:38:11,706
<i>Awak orang yang saya ambil berat.</i>

391
00:38:12,957 --> 00:38:15,293
<i>Saya lega awak akan tinggal</i>
<i>bersama Park So-hyeon.</i>

392
00:38:15,876 --> 00:38:19,088
Apabila saya tinggalkan kerja ini,
saya terfikir kenapa rasa kosong.

393
00:38:20,381 --> 00:38:22,383
Sebab awak sentiasa ada di setiap langkah.

394
00:38:23,467 --> 00:38:25,761
<i>Tanpa pandangan awak,</i>

395
00:38:25,845 --> 00:38:28,055
<i>saya hilang arah dan impian.</i>

396
00:38:28,139 --> 00:38:30,057
<i>Saya nak jalani hidup biasa,</i>

397
00:38:31,851 --> 00:38:34,562
tetapi akhirnya memaksa diri
untuk seiring dengan awak.

398
00:38:36,022 --> 00:38:37,356
<i>Sepuluh tahun hidup saya</i>

399
00:38:39,191 --> 00:38:41,402
hanya awak tahu betapa kuat saya bekerja.

400
00:38:43,154 --> 00:38:44,905
Itu saya boleh sahkan.

401
00:38:45,781 --> 00:38:50,286
<i>Saya boleh sahkan awak dah beri segalanya.</i>

402
00:38:51,287 --> 00:38:52,455
Itu dah cukup bagi saya.

403
00:38:56,417 --> 00:38:57,835
Jaga diri.

404
00:39:00,171 --> 00:39:01,172
<i>Awak juga.</i>

405
00:39:02,923 --> 00:39:06,927
Ucap selamat tinggal dalam telefon
tak adalah teruk sangat.

406
00:39:08,679 --> 00:39:09,930
Terima kasih,

407
00:39:11,682 --> 00:39:12,850
Seong-chan.

408
00:39:12,933 --> 00:39:14,185
<i>Terima kasih juga.</i>

409
00:39:15,353 --> 00:39:16,187
<i>Saya letak dulu.</i>

410
00:39:29,950 --> 00:39:31,118
Marilah.

411
00:39:36,040 --> 00:39:38,334
Selamat Tahun Baru.

412
00:40:53,617 --> 00:40:57,288
SELAMAT HARI JADI
9 NOVEMBER 2024

413
00:41:27,318 --> 00:41:29,236
Penting sangatkah

414
00:41:30,905 --> 00:41:32,281
laci separuh terbuka?

415
00:41:34,742 --> 00:41:36,035
Adakah ini…

416
00:41:38,954 --> 00:41:41,040
Adakah ini memang

417
00:41:42,458 --> 00:41:44,168
sesakit ini?

418
00:41:46,754 --> 00:41:49,840
Ayah nak bernafas pun susah
macam lari maraton,

419
00:41:49,924 --> 00:41:51,842
kau di sini merungut…

420
00:42:05,314 --> 00:42:06,398
<i>Dalam perjalanan.</i>

421
00:42:06,482 --> 00:42:07,483
Tak apa.

422
00:42:08,400 --> 00:42:09,860
Tak payah jumpa hari ini.

423
00:42:28,420 --> 00:42:30,256
Pemilik kereta 2017.

424
00:42:39,848 --> 00:42:41,183
Pemilik kereta 2017?

425
00:42:42,393 --> 00:42:43,894
Helo? Ada orang di rumah?

426
00:42:45,688 --> 00:42:47,106
Pemilik kereta 2017?

427
00:42:47,189 --> 00:42:48,649
A-sol?

428
00:42:50,025 --> 00:42:51,318
Kenapa?

429
00:42:52,111 --> 00:42:54,280
Saya nak keluarkan kereta, tak ada orang.

430
00:43:01,453 --> 00:43:03,747
Hai, mak. Saya sibuk. Nanti saya telefon.

431
00:43:08,544 --> 00:43:09,587
Ya.

432
00:43:10,337 --> 00:43:12,590
Tak, saya tak sibuk. Saya datang sekarang.

433
00:43:14,258 --> 00:43:15,259
Mak, jangan menangis.

434
00:43:17,261 --> 00:43:18,304
Okey.

435
00:43:21,724 --> 00:43:22,933
Kereta…

436
00:43:23,684 --> 00:43:25,102
Suruh mereka alih.

437
00:43:26,228 --> 00:43:29,148
Saya kena pergi jumpa ayah.

438
00:43:33,736 --> 00:43:34,570
A-sol.

439
00:44:03,223 --> 00:44:05,893
Sekarang dia okey.

440
00:44:08,228 --> 00:44:11,690
Mak kata dia akan alami keadaan begini
dan akan pulih semula,

441
00:44:11,774 --> 00:44:13,567
dia minta saya bawa pakaian.

442
00:44:14,151 --> 00:44:15,402
Ada apa-apa saya boleh tolong?

443
00:44:16,236 --> 00:44:17,863
Saya tinggal di rumah awak.

444
00:44:19,823 --> 00:44:21,158
Tapi tak sangka pula begini.

445
00:44:22,076 --> 00:44:23,577
Nanti awak masuk awak tahulah.

446
00:44:24,161 --> 00:44:27,206
Saya bawa sekarang
supaya awak boleh buat sikit-sikit,

447
00:44:29,124 --> 00:44:30,751
tapi nampaknya awak kena buat cepat.

448
00:44:33,545 --> 00:44:34,463
Okey.

449
00:44:35,547 --> 00:44:36,590
Saya pergi dulu.

450
00:44:37,841 --> 00:44:38,967
Tae-seo.

451
00:44:40,386 --> 00:44:41,804
Beberapa hari lepas,

452
00:44:41,887 --> 00:44:43,681
wanita yang naik basikal itu…

453
00:44:46,058 --> 00:44:47,893
Dia datang ke rumah awak.

454
00:44:50,104 --> 00:44:52,606
Saya patutnya ambil kereta saja,

455
00:44:52,690 --> 00:44:54,942
tapi saya naik ke rumah awak
macam orang bodoh

456
00:44:56,193 --> 00:44:57,403
dan masukkan kata laluan.

457
00:44:59,279 --> 00:45:01,448
Tapi masa saya turun, dia dah tak ada.

458
00:45:02,032 --> 00:45:03,534
Mesti saya dah gila.

459
00:45:10,582 --> 00:45:11,417
Saya minta maaf.

460
00:45:17,339 --> 00:45:18,257
Tae-seo.

461
00:45:19,675 --> 00:45:21,468
Giliran saya untuk dengar.

462
00:45:24,012 --> 00:45:25,931
Saya betul-betul kena sedia.

463
00:45:27,099 --> 00:45:28,642
Saya tak ada…

464
00:45:30,144 --> 00:45:32,479
Saya tak ada banyak masa.

465
00:45:35,482 --> 00:45:38,527
Beritahu apa yang awak nak ucap

466
00:45:39,736 --> 00:45:40,988
terima kasih sekarang.

467
00:45:41,905 --> 00:45:43,282
Saya nak dengar sekarang.

468
00:45:53,667 --> 00:45:56,462
Awak nak pergi berjalan?

469
00:46:15,272 --> 00:46:16,273
Saya bersyukur

470
00:46:17,774 --> 00:46:19,026
kepada awak

471
00:46:22,946 --> 00:46:24,198
sebab sekarang

472
00:46:26,783 --> 00:46:28,911
saya boleh harapkan
perpisahan yang hangat.

473
00:46:33,165 --> 00:46:34,291
Awak pun tahu…

474
00:47:18,085 --> 00:47:21,922
<i>Kalau tiga detik menunggu</i>
<i>untuk hasilkan satu bingkai</i>

475
00:47:22,005 --> 00:47:23,882
<i>boleh siap dalam sehari</i>…

476
00:47:25,467 --> 00:47:28,387
- Apa yang saya sebut itu…
- Tanda nama saya?

477
00:47:28,470 --> 00:47:30,722
JULAI 2014

478
00:47:30,806 --> 00:47:31,640
Terima kasih.

479
00:47:31,723 --> 00:47:34,226
PUSAT BELAJAR MAEUM

480
00:47:37,604 --> 00:47:38,564
<i>…saya akan percaya</i>

481
00:47:40,065 --> 00:47:42,818
<i>sokongan ikhlas yang saya beri dulu</i>

482
00:47:42,901 --> 00:47:47,531
<i>akhirnya kembali kepada saya.</i>

483
00:47:56,081 --> 00:47:58,458
<i>Guna </i>hanji<i> untuk alas</i>

484
00:47:58,542 --> 00:48:00,377
<i>dan kayu oak untuk bingkai.</i>

485
00:48:01,753 --> 00:48:06,341
<i>Saya nak wajah ayah</i>
<i>terasa dipeluk dengan hangat.</i>

486
00:48:09,386 --> 00:48:10,429
<i>Tolong, ya?</i>

487
00:48:44,087 --> 00:48:46,089
Salji dah reda.

488
00:48:51,219 --> 00:48:55,223
Nampaknya tadi salji turun
untuk nenek kamu.

489
00:49:00,228 --> 00:49:03,148
<i>Ingatan nenek Hui-seo datang dan pergi?</i>

490
00:49:03,815 --> 00:49:05,984
Doktor kata otaknya dalam pemulihan.

491
00:49:06,068 --> 00:49:09,071
Buat masa ini, ingatannya bercampur,
tapi akan kembali semula.

492
00:49:12,574 --> 00:49:15,994
Apabila usia meningkat,
10 tahun lalu terasa seperti semalam

493
00:49:16,078 --> 00:49:18,622
dan semalam pula terasa jauh.

494
00:49:20,415 --> 00:49:21,792
Fikiran jadi bercelaru.

495
00:49:25,712 --> 00:49:27,089
Mereka datang.

496
00:49:51,655 --> 00:49:52,864
Mana dia?

497
00:49:52,948 --> 00:49:54,991
Saya di sini.

498
00:49:56,243 --> 00:49:57,369
Selamat pulang.

499
00:49:59,454 --> 00:50:00,288
Mana Eun-a?

500
00:50:02,624 --> 00:50:04,710
Kalau Eun-a, maksudnya 10 tahun lepas.

501
00:50:05,919 --> 00:50:07,462
Hwa-sun.

502
00:50:07,546 --> 00:50:08,797
Kenapa cari Eun-a?

503
00:50:13,844 --> 00:50:15,345
Eun-a.

504
00:50:18,014 --> 00:50:19,891
Eun-a!

505
00:50:26,064 --> 00:50:27,149
Eun-a.

506
00:50:28,734 --> 00:50:30,193
Beri tangan awak.

507
00:50:30,277 --> 00:50:32,863
Aduhai, awak kaut salji.

508
00:50:32,946 --> 00:50:34,573
Awak tak apa-apa?

509
00:50:37,409 --> 00:50:41,121
Dia fikir hari ini kamu kaut salji.

510
00:50:42,998 --> 00:50:44,833
Awak rasa Tae-seo selamat sampai?

511
00:50:44,916 --> 00:50:47,127
Saya tak tahu. Saya pun risau.

512
00:50:55,093 --> 00:50:58,513
<i>Awak dah bersihkan salji dari trak kita.</i>

513
00:50:59,222 --> 00:51:01,600
Kami terpaksa hantar Tae-seo masuk tentera
seorang diri.

514
00:51:02,476 --> 00:51:05,145
Kami tak boleh buat apa-apa.

515
00:51:07,981 --> 00:51:09,733
Sakit, bukan?

516
00:51:11,902 --> 00:51:15,489
Memang sakit sangat,
tapi sekarang saya dah okey.

517
00:51:16,281 --> 00:51:17,824
Baguslah.

518
00:51:17,908 --> 00:51:19,743
Bagus.

519
00:51:19,826 --> 00:51:21,328
Dengar kata nak ke Hawaii.

520
00:51:23,205 --> 00:51:24,998
Selamat jalan.

521
00:51:25,081 --> 00:51:30,045
Kami akan jenguk ayah awak
supaya dia tak sunyi.

522
00:51:31,463 --> 00:51:35,050
Dah lama nenek nak cakap.
Dah lama terbeban di hati.

523
00:51:38,470 --> 00:51:40,472
Terima kasih.

524
00:52:16,800 --> 00:52:17,968
Nenek?

525
00:52:19,052 --> 00:52:21,096
Ini saya, Tae-seo.

526
00:52:21,179 --> 00:52:23,056
Ingat saya, bukan?

527
00:52:23,139 --> 00:52:24,683
<i>Kenapa pula tak ingat?</i>

528
00:52:25,600 --> 00:52:27,185
Nenek dah balik dengan selamat.

529
00:52:32,107 --> 00:52:33,316
Eun-a!

530
00:52:37,237 --> 00:52:39,072
Nenek dah balik.

531
00:52:39,155 --> 00:52:41,366
- Bukan dari 10 tahun lepas. Sekarang.
- Apa?

532
00:52:42,576 --> 00:52:43,660
Naik.

533
00:52:43,743 --> 00:52:45,787
Sekarang. Masa kini!

534
00:52:45,871 --> 00:52:47,789
Ya, saya dah faham.

535
00:52:52,294 --> 00:52:55,297
Sungai Han ada banyak jambatan, bukan?

536
00:52:55,380 --> 00:52:56,631
Sangat panjang.

537
00:52:57,632 --> 00:52:58,675
Lari di sana setiap hari?

538
00:52:59,718 --> 00:53:02,429
<i>Saya banyak duduk masa kendalikan tren,</i>

539
00:53:03,722 --> 00:53:06,016
<i>jadi itu cara saya bersenam.</i>

540
00:53:07,142 --> 00:53:08,143
Begitu. Baguslah.

541
00:53:08,226 --> 00:53:11,021
Kamu kena jaga kesihatan sambil bekerja.

542
00:53:12,147 --> 00:53:13,440
<i>Aduhai, Eun-a!</i>

543
00:53:14,107 --> 00:53:15,525
<i>Nenek apa khabar?</i>

544
00:53:17,777 --> 00:53:20,196
Eun-a. Aduhai, Eun-a.

545
00:53:20,280 --> 00:53:21,573
Selamat kembali.

546
00:53:22,741 --> 00:53:25,827
<i>Awak langsung tak berubah.</i>

547
00:53:25,911 --> 00:53:27,787
<i>Nenek pun tak berubah juga.</i>

548
00:53:29,080 --> 00:53:31,374
<i>Biar saya ikat semula skarf ini.</i>

549
00:53:33,001 --> 00:53:37,714
<i>Pusing-pusing kemudian ikat.</i>

550
00:53:37,797 --> 00:53:39,132
<i>Dah siap. Barulah hangat.</i>

551
00:53:41,593 --> 00:53:45,680
<i>Semua orang di sini risaukan awak.</i>

552
00:53:45,764 --> 00:53:48,433
<i>Baguslah awak dah balik.</i>

553
00:53:48,516 --> 00:53:49,726
<i>Bagus.</i>

554
00:54:13,875 --> 00:54:16,503
<i>Saya hantar awak esok.</i>

555
00:54:17,420 --> 00:54:18,630
<i>Kita ucap selamat tinggal.</i>

556
00:54:30,976 --> 00:54:32,268
- Nenek.
- Ya?

557
00:54:32,352 --> 00:54:34,020
Baik-baik walaupun saya tak ada.

558
00:54:34,688 --> 00:54:36,731
Nenek akan sunyi saya pergi tiba-tiba.

559
00:54:36,815 --> 00:54:37,649
Itulah.

560
00:54:37,732 --> 00:54:39,901
Nenek seronok kebelakangan ini

561
00:54:39,985 --> 00:54:42,529
asyik makan dan tidur saja setiap hari.

562
00:54:42,612 --> 00:54:44,698
Lepas habis berseronok,
kena teruskan hidup.

563
00:54:45,323 --> 00:54:47,784
Tak boleh asyik teringat, okey?

564
00:54:48,368 --> 00:54:49,536
Betul.

565
00:54:55,458 --> 00:54:56,876
Terima kasih, nenek.

566
00:55:03,091 --> 00:55:04,009
Jom ambil gambar.

567
00:55:04,092 --> 00:55:05,885
- Gambar?
- Ya.

568
00:55:05,969 --> 00:55:07,554
Gambar lebih cantik ada pokok.

569
00:55:10,974 --> 00:55:13,435
- Saya akan tengok setiap hari.
- Okey.

570
00:55:14,269 --> 00:55:16,104
Senyum cakap "Eun-a".

571
00:55:16,688 --> 00:55:19,816
Mo Eun-a.

572
00:55:24,112 --> 00:55:27,157
Cantiknya. Saya akan tengok setiap hari.

573
00:55:52,557 --> 00:55:55,560
<i>Saya akan pergi ke Stesen Dongjak.</i>

574
00:56:00,607 --> 00:56:03,109
<i>Stesen Dongjak ke Incheon dekat sangat.</i>

575
00:57:30,405 --> 00:57:31,448
YEON NAMSAN

576
00:57:36,286 --> 00:57:38,580
<i>Itu pemandangan rutin saya setiap hari.</i>

577
00:57:41,291 --> 00:57:42,625
<i>Awak kata nak tengok.</i>

578
00:57:59,142 --> 00:57:59,976
<i>Saya…</i>

579
00:58:01,519 --> 00:58:04,564
<i>akan buat apa yang kita</i>
<i>nak buat sama-sama.</i>

580
00:58:06,816 --> 00:58:08,902
<i>Awak sebab saya dapat buat keputusan,</i>

581
00:58:09,486 --> 00:58:11,196
<i>jadi saya akan tunggu awak di sana.</i>

582
00:58:12,030 --> 00:58:17,118
<i>Pergi sana, disayangi dan dihargai</i>

583
00:58:17,202 --> 00:58:18,786
<i>dan jalani hidup yang hebat.</i>

584
00:58:19,621 --> 00:58:21,039
<i>Kalau suatu hari</i>

585
00:58:21,706 --> 00:58:24,042
<i>awak terfikir tentang masa depan</i>
<i>yang ada saya,</i>

586
00:58:25,585 --> 00:58:26,836
<i>beritahu saya.</i>

587
00:58:53,363 --> 00:58:55,073
Kita berpisah di sini.

588
00:59:05,208 --> 00:59:06,709
Terima kasih hantar saya.

589
00:59:08,670 --> 00:59:09,504
Ini…

590
00:59:11,297 --> 00:59:14,175
kali pertama kita ucap
selamat tinggal depan-depan.

591
00:59:18,763 --> 00:59:20,306
Selamat tinggal.

592
00:59:31,734 --> 00:59:33,111
Selamat jalan.

593
01:00:00,221 --> 01:00:01,514
Saya cintakan awak,

594
01:00:04,934 --> 01:00:05,893
Mo Eun-a.

595
01:00:38,926 --> 01:00:42,305
Tuan-tuan dan puan-puan,
stesen seterusnya adalah…

596
01:00:55,234 --> 01:00:57,695
Luangkan sedikit masa melihat ke tingkap.

597
01:01:14,754 --> 01:01:16,839
<i>Pemandangan biasa dalam hidup kita</i>

598
01:01:18,841 --> 01:01:21,302
<i>boleh jadi cahaya tak terlupakan</i>

599
01:01:22,470 --> 01:01:23,680
<i>yang membawa kita</i>

600
01:01:26,057 --> 01:01:27,266
<i>dengan cara tertentu</i>

601
01:01:28,476 --> 01:01:30,645
<i>dan kepada seseorang.</i>

602
01:01:34,691 --> 01:01:36,067
<i>Saya harap hari ini</i>

603
01:01:36,150 --> 01:01:38,778
<i>satu lagi hari bermakna</i>

604
01:01:39,487 --> 01:01:41,948
<i>di mana anda ikut cahaya dalam diri.</i>

605
01:01:43,658 --> 01:01:44,701
<i>Anda harungi hari ini</i>

606
01:01:46,369 --> 01:01:47,954
<i>dengan cukup hebat.</i>

607
01:01:53,668 --> 01:01:55,420
Stesen seterusnya adalah…

